    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver at an accessible price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a minor dent on the rear passenger side. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays typical wear on the upholstery and some aging on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need a routine suspension service and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag.",
