    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always garage-kept, strictly hand-washed, and treated with nothing but the best. It honestly looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you really go looking for it, but in my eyes, she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate her as much as I have. Come on by, let\u2019s chat cars, and you can see for yourself!",
